Assumption Auto-tools build information
=======================================

Instruction to build the assumption fixtures with the auto-tools

ssh://orri@gos.sagos.is:22/home/git/assumption

Depends
-------

- C++ compiler
- Autoconf
- Automake
- Libtool

Build
-----

Generate all the necessary build scripts by running

    autoreconf -ivf

       -i, --install
              copy missing auxiliary files

       -i, --install
              copy missing auxiliary files

       -v, --verbose
              verbosely report processing


With these in place then

    ./configure
    make

Run the tests with

    make check

Author: Geirmundur Orri Sigurdsson <orri@icesoft.is>
26 September 2018
